    {
      "id": "bridge-editor-contract-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Overview",
      "position": {
        "x": 780,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Bridge Editor Surface\n\nThe editor should be sectioned by authority, not by storage fields. Authors need to see what source is targeted, what actions are granted, what artifacts are exposed, and what the effective result will be."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-editor-contract-source",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Source Section",
      "position": {
        "x": 780,
        "y": 20
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Source\n\nThe first section should own:\n\n- `ref`\n- `resourceKind`\n- resolved target summary\n- quick open to source\n\nThis section answers: what artifact is the bridge pointed at?"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-editor-contract-grants",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Grants Section",
      "position": {
        "x": 1260,
        "y": -260
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Grants\n\nThe second section should expose grants as explicit actions.\n\nRecommended controls:\n\n- `create`\n- `consume-view`\n- `runtime`\n\nThis section answers: what operations are permitted?"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-editor-contract-exposure",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Exposure Section",
      "position": {
        "x": 1260,
        "y": 20
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Exposure\n\nThe third section should own one policy row per family:\n\n- `nodes`\n- `edges`\n- `views`\n- `scripts`\n- `declarations`\n\nEach row needs:\n\n- mode selector: `deny`, `allow`, `allowlist`, `denylist`\n- include / exclude entry field when the mode requires it"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-editor-contract-effective",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Effective Result",
      "position": {
        "x": 1740,
        "y": -120
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Effective Result\n\nThe last section should be read-only.\n\nIt should summarize what the bridge is actually making available, for example:\n\n- can create from 2 node classes\n- can consume 1 named view\n- scripts denied\n\nThis section is the sanity check."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-editor-contract-port-exposure",
      "type": "port",
      "label": "Bridge Exposure Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": 1740,
